"And this experience that we would consider in this case by imagining the birth of a child in a foreign environment will result in the return to Earth of a disabled child, completely disadapted," predicts the Director of the Bioethics Committee of the Institute of Medical-Biological Problems of the Russian Academy of Sciences, P. Igor.
